lliam halsey on march   halsey appeared as a mystery guest on episode no  of the game show whats my line where the panel correctly deduced his identity in the television series mchales navy one of captain binghamptons catchphrases whenever he would get frustrated with one of mchales schemes was what in the name of halsey is going on here admiral halsey is mentioned in the film the hunt for red october soviet submarine commander marko ramius while engaged in battle with the soviet attack submarine konovalov asks jack ryan what book he wrote for the cia ryan replies that it was about admiral halsey entitled the fighting sailor not to be confused with a real book of the same title ramius reveals his awareness of the book and expresses disdain for ryans assessment of halsey saying your conclusions were all wrong ryan halsey acted stupidly the fictional aircraft carrier uss william halsey in darren sapps novel fire on the flight deck is named for halsey see alsoedit biography portal list of fleet and grand admirals list of united states military leaders by rank list of military figures by nickname referencesedit notes  the big blue fleet was the name given to the main fleet of the us navy in the pacific the term stems from prewar planning called the color plans because each nation included was given a color code name in these potential plans the british navy was red the german navy black and so forth the imperial japanese navy was termed the orange fleet the us fleet was the blue fleet the big blue fleet was the massive fleet that the us navy anticipated they would win the war with it was thought this fleet would largely come into being by late  early   this view however was not held by chester nimitz who told spruance he had done exactly the right thing citations  us officers holding fivestar rank never retire they draw full active duty pay for lifespencer c tucker  the encyclopedia of the vietnam war a political social and military history abcclio pp  isbn    halsey arlingtoncemeterynet  a b morison the struggle for guadalcanal p  a b c potter p   berger meyer home town roars salute to halsey the commander of the third fleet returns to his hometown in new jersey new pingry boys cheer white horse atop cake the new york times november   retrieved february    johnson bill  seven societys secret still secret washington post pp c   wukovits john  admiral bull halsey palgrave macmillan p  isbn    borneman page   a b c d e f wukovits john  admiral bull halsey the life and wars of the navys most controversial commander isbn    fleet admiral william frederick halsey jr naval historical center   borneman page   morison the rising sun in the pacific page   wildenberg thomas midway sheer luck or better doctrine naval college war review winter  vol  no  wildenberg quotes brownings thesis every carrier we have knows what it means to be bopped with all planes on deck because her hands were tied by uncertainty as to her next move  a b books the general and the admiral time november     millis page   j bryan  admiral halseys story whittlesey house pp – isbn    potter bull halsey  potter nimitz page   potter nimitz page   potter nimitz page   potter bull halsey p   morison p – frank p – dull p –  richard frank  guadalcanal the definitive account of the landmark battle penguin books isbn    seal jon and michael ahn an interview with joseph jacob joe foss at the wayback machine archived february   microsoft games studios march  retrieved august    taylor p   potter bull halsey p   potter admiral arleigh burke pp   parshall and tully shattered sword pp –  cutler the battle of leyte gulf p   tuohy william  americas fighting admiralswinning the war at sea in world war ii zenith press p  isbn    hone thomas winter  replacing battleships with aircraft carriers in the pacific in world war ii naval war college review p  retrieved  april    a b c d willmott h p six the great day of wrath the battle of leyte gulf the last fleet action indiana university pres