trategic income etf first trust alphadex canadian dividend etf first trust exchangetraded fund iv  first trust senior loan fund and first trust series fund  first trust short duration high income fund he served as portfolio manager of first trust short duration high yield bond etf mr housey is a part of the leveraged finance team at the firm he previously served as an executive director and portfolio manager at van kampen funds inc earlier mr housey served as a portfolio manager of structured products and senior analyst in the senior loan group at the firm he has extensive experience in portfolio management of both leveraged and unleveraged credit products including senior loans highyield bonds credit derivatives and corporate restructurings mr houusey also has extensive retail and institutional fund raising experience he serves on the village of glen ellyn il police pension board mr housey is a member of the cfa institute and the cfa society of chicago he holds the finra series  series  and series  licenses he holds the chartered financial analyst designation mr housey received an mba in finance management and strategy from northwestern universitys kellogg school of business and a bs in finance from eastern illinois universityread full background corporate headquarters  east liberty drivewheaton illinois united statesphone fax  board members memberships there is no board members memberships data available education bs eastern illinois universitymba jl kellogg school of management northwestern university other affiliations eastern illinois universityfirst trust advisors lpjl kellogg school of management northwestern universityfirst trust senior floating rate income fund iifirst trust short duration high yield bond etf cadhedgedfirst trust exchangetraded fund iv  first trust senior loan fundfirst trust series fund  first trust short duration high income fundfirst trust exchangetraded fund iv  first trust tactical high yield etffirst trust alphadex canadian dividend e